&lt;li&gt;Oversee the design, implementation, and deployment of robust, scalable computational pipelines for multi-omics data analysis, ensuring accuracy, reproducibility, and maintainability&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide scientific input into platform strategy, translating computational insights into actionable directions for the broader team&lt;/li&gt;
