&lt;li&gt;Maintain and troubleshoot equipment to ensure consistency and continuity of operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document, analyze and present experimental results internally and externally&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with CDMOs and provide technology transfer support to facilitate scale up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interface with cross-functional teams to ensure programs are on track and stakeholders’ needs are met&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate and reliable record keeping including database management, batch records, notebooks, and all other pertinent documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
